cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as entity and relation extraction. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel hierarchical multi-task tagging model for joint extraction of entities and relations. It could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as knowledge graph construction is a common task in information retrieval. Finally, it may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the proposed model uses neural networks for learning semantic representations.
